## Gate C Purpose
<!-- Gate C authorises closure of Phase 3 and transition to Phase 4 (Build & Integration). -->
Gate C validates that all Phase 3 design artefacts are complete, internally consistent,
and meet the acceptance criteria defined at Gate B. The approved design becomes the
authoritative input for Phase 4.

